        <div class="feat"><div class="feat-icon">🌍</div><div><strong>Pan-India Reach</strong><p>Jobs across 500+ cities from Tier 1 metros to emerging towns.</p></div></div>
      </div>

      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-teal">Get in Touch →</a>
